<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/register.css">
    <script src="/js/home/register.js" defer></script>
    
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="register_menu">
        <form>
            <a href="/"><div class="header_logo"></div></a>
            <div class="input_area">
                <input type="text" id="id" name="id" autocomplete="off" required>
                <label for="id">아이디</label>
            </div>
            
            <div class="input_area">
                <input type="password" id="psword" name="psword" autocomplete="off" required>
                <label for="psword">비밀번호</label>
            </div>
            <div class="input_area">
                <input type="password" id="psword_confirm" name="psword_confirm" autocomplete="off" required>
                <label for="psword_confirm">비밀번호 확인</label>
            </div>

            <div class="input_area">
                <input type="text" id="name" name="name" autocomplete="off" required>
                <label for="name">이름</label>
            </div>


            <div class="input_area2">
                <input type="text" id="sms_certify" name="sms_certify" autocomplete="off" required placeholder="휴대폰 번호를 입력하세요." >
                <label for="sms_certify">휴대폰 인증</label>
                <p id="button">인증번호 전송</p>
            </div>

            <div class="input_area">
                <input type="text" id="authnom" name="authnom" autocomplete="off" required placeholder="인증번호를 입력하세요.">
            </div>
            <p id="rgs_btn">가입하기</p>
            <p class="msg">이미 회원가입을 했나요? <a href="/login">로그인</a></p>
        </form>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <ul>
            <li>개인정보처리방침 등</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</body>
</html>